A simple module to replace `Backbone.sync` with *sessionStorage*-based
persistence. Models are given GUIDS, and saved into a JSON object. Simple
as that.

this is from backbone-localstorage - but I have a need to use sessionStorage, utilizing amplify.js

see http://documentcloud.github.com/backbone/docs/backbone-localstorage.html
see http://amplifyjs.com/api/store/